幾星期先消瘀<br />\n<br />\n中一放學打波 隔離有學校足球隊練波踢左個足球過黎 我幫手執個陣足球隊有條撚頭跑過黎一腳踢落個波度 踢中埋我隻右手 對唔住都無聲 我右手中指第一節骨裂"},{"pid":"8f3ca4f64d048b9e395a08d0b3cac48d3c849954","tid":123142,"uid":64271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T16:53:41.000Z","msg":"以前細個個fd玩鋼筋揮出去果下打中左個額頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爆晒光,返到屋企仲好撚驚,見止左血醫院都冇去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a44b2edae1212f4ef08df3feec6c584a534305","tid":123142,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T16:55:37.000Z","msg":"細個個陣喺油站執到隻俾人遺棄既大狗翻黎養 <br />\n但佢有少少情緒唔穩定 <br />\n有次細佬d野食俾隻狗食咗 佢就拎藤條打我隻狗<br />\n我沖上前擋 結果隻狗發狂咬錯咗我 成隻左手都係血<br />\n最後我老母求其倒咗成半支消毒火酒就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而隻狗就俾我爸送走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1e598e6a00294dad75b3f74e1ba68d82d5659b","tid":123142,"uid":74043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:03:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>暗戀一個人兩年 最後佢中意咗我個fd</blockquote><br />\n叫春返感情台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw，細個睇卡通片見啲角色可以用把遮當降落傘用<br />\n之後就有樣學樣係三樓天台(住村屋)跳左落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醒返已經係醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個咁高都唔死<br />\n樓下有冇嘢？</blockquote><br />\n如果用腳落底應該骨折姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 冇讀過bio"},{"pid":"d70ccad34c38d8d8141f0a19343465adad49e9b3","tid":123142,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:09:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腳趾公踢到啲防火門<br />\n流左超多血 腳甲仲鬆鬆地<br />\n過幾日成塊甩埋 生返塊好細塊同好軟嘅腳甲<br />\n之後先慢慢硬返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇黎好多人都爆腳甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84dd5d83ea7fb83d222d366710f19ca9821ba4e","tid":123142,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:10:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>暗戀一個人兩年 最後佢中意咗我個fd</blockquote><br />\n叫春返感情台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw，細個睇卡通片見啲角色可以用把遮當降落傘用<br />\n之後就有樣學樣係三樓天台(住村屋)跳左落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醒返已經係醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴線返青山啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上咩連登"},{"pid":"6c1afd124057bce5cd6e8024954e785f9cf61019","tid":123142,"uid":35034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:13:19.000Z","msg":"他知道，哭是沒有用的。"},{"pid":"e90332d9aefbf09dbf58cfc24493109216f133f7","tid":123142,"uid":22731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:19:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比輕鐵車到<br />\n個身斷咗兩節<br />\n好彩賠左粒賢者之石比我<br />\n最後冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係真係痛撚到就黎死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n救唔返最多做合成獸姐 冇咩嘅</blockquote><br />\n講還講 下家咪撚貼圖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e9c79bd8355b06e6dc4a7294994527a2293594","tid":123142,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:26:28.000Z","msg":"細個係張凳跌咗落牆角之後個頭後腦落地<br />\n流咗勁多血入到醫院比畀返藍色嘅布擒住先知道自己入咗醫院仲要feel到個頭有啲凍冰冰嘅野搞緊我原來係比護士縫針勁痛，到而家都唔知發生咩事係屋企人話俾我知我先知原來個頭有忽無左頭髮係咁樣得來"},{"pid":"72ab451bcbe23aa42ca529ddea3a7c557f9163cb","tid":123142,"uid":27785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:27:59.000Z","msg":"兩年內甩左5次臼，最後要做手術先搞得掂"},{"pid":"dcbebee27e160aecd4e8c23f8c6ced668a0b66f1","tid":123142,"uid":21679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:35:56.000Z","msg":"理應就係細個跳床跌親個鼻撞落枱角縫五針最嚴重<br />\n但冇記憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有記憶應該係一年前跑跑下比人kick跌膝頭狠狠地撞落地下<br />\n一整親個下痛到腳震 行唔到<br />\n忍左一晚樓梯都行唔到去左睇跌打<br />\n話係扭傷韌帶腫左之類<br />\n依家間唔中會痛 跪唔到 撳落去都仲會痛<br />\n但冇理已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e6a272feee56a3469ec27657532dfdcb82a042","tid":123142,"uid":58699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:38:31.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"7dbb0abc83320449e282b74aedd80ff0ccb95d26","tid":123142,"uid":57090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:43:17.000Z","msg":"依個post睇到我成身軟唒 手同腳痺唒 出唔到力"},{"pid":"311fd2469e3a16164242933b0c0f6650d93b4b48","tid":123142,"uid":79744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:46:57.000Z","msg":"擤鼻涕太用力擤損左個鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177ad62cc9e56323adb641a3c9bf721a4e8d60ca","tid":123142,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他知道，哭是沒有用的。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n刮痧定縫針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55f613f41b0dab8d7f968b33535aa66e17bd70a","tid":123142,"uid":2177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:51:42.000Z","msg":"俾滾水淥親大脾"},{"pid":"e945dc7351cbe7ca53fdb99398acea4abdf3f23b","tid":123142,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:59:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60f181bb9f363607ac16b4be67ca9aab24ccad71","tid":123142,"uid":35539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:03:17.000Z","msg":"見唔到玻璃 沖埋去撞頭<br />\n係街向後望 一轉頭就頭撞電燈柱<br />\n有人打爛玻璃杯 無睇到 踩到一地血<br />\n腳指尾勾住梳化腳 痛到甩出黎"},{"pid":"eaa764adc39382f773bbc0033b8127015e478d8a","tid":123142,"uid":4244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:14:37.00