r />\n<br />\n隻腳差唔多兩星期先好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57bc7e816d55a6e2170acb1803b7cb920abc756","tid":123142,"uid":82940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同朋友猜輸咗 要用枝牙籤塞落腳趾公到 之後一野踢落牆到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係塞係腳甲入面</blockquote><br />\n我屌你老母 睇到隻腳縮左一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20578cc6a328f063dc52c097ab7bad1c9d0e2651","tid":123142,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:34:14.000Z","msg":"踩單車炒車<br />\n撞裂左手腕舊骨同移位<br />\n做手術"},{"pid":"c6adf184492248abc4568ad43128cd4d5f23374f","tid":123142,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:36:59.000Z","msg":"個頭甩咗"},{"pid":"7c8ab72df2104cae650a80d9a137305482b4a4c5","tid":123142,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:40:27.000Z","msg":"溜冰 貪玩 尾指 吊下吊下 差少少就切埋神經就無 <br />\n當晚下一日係一個等同內定既亞洲杯青年港隊選拔（因為人數=名額） 就咁錯過左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n仲話一壞死就要切 好彩依加咩野都無"},{"pid":"d84b324b68a5c73cce0e6535cb6f90d05cb31e85","tid":123142,"uid":61979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:46:17.000Z","msg":"細個訓訓下教碌咗落床,咁啱有隻唔知咩手辦公仔係地下,成個下巴吉落去,插穿咗,嗰下完全未sense到發生咩事,又上返床訓,跟住老豆出嚟睇吓咩料先發現,仲記得好似成個枕頭都係血,變哂紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7d442ad3c4fdf77d5c2daa7f7db041fb519416","tid":123142,"uid":5691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:46:28.000Z","msg":"係油站食緊飯同fd傾計 <br />\n點知個fd接受唔到自己條女係臭雞呢個事實，仲無啦啦打我<br />\n搞到我鼻血一個月流一次<br />\n好彩因為咁條女特別照顧左我一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" c